00:05:08.570 --> 00:05:10.640 align:middle line:84%
Another study is
published that says,

00:05:10.640 --> 00:05:13.130 align:middle line:90%
vitamins don't help very much.

00:05:13.130 --> 00:05:14.510 align:middle line:84%
And you have this
back and forth.

00:05:14.510 --> 00:05:16.640 align:middle line:84%
But the problem is because
all of those studies

00:05:16.640 --> 00:05:18.920 align:middle line:90%
