00:05:47.060 --> 00:05:49.220 align:middle line:90%
vitamins is new knowledge.

00:05:49.220 --> 00:05:50.690 align:middle line:90%
But that's the answer.

00:05:50.690 --> 00:05:52.520 align:middle line:84%
The cause of
cardiovascular disease,

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:56.330 align:middle line:84%
therefore, is a failure to
take the vitamins and a failure

00:05:56.330 --> 00:05:57.380 align:middle line:90%
to eat right.

00:05:57.380 --> 00:05:59.630 align:middle line:84%
The good news is
that even people

00:05:59.630 --> 00:06:03.110 align:middle line:84%
with advanced cardiovascular
disease, when they start

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:05.570 align:middle line:84%
taking the nutrients and
they change their diet,

00:06:05.570 --> 00:06:09.010 align:middle line:84%
